Module com.example.samplesalad
Package com.example.samplesalad.model

Class ProjectLoader

java.lang.Object
com.example.samplesalad.model.ProjectLoader
public class ProjectLoader extends Object
The ProjectLoader class is responsible for loading a music project from the database, including all its associated sequencers, patterns, and pad events.

      projectDAO - The DAO for accessing project data.
